The paper discusses the security vulnerabilities of smartphones and focuses on steganography techniques, which fall under the category of information hiding. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Additionally, the paper also discusses the use of software applications for embedding secret data, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the different covert channels used for steganography, which can fall under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
